snippet.title: Taiko no Tatsujin: Rhythm Festival - Gameplay Trailer #2: DON-chan Band
snippet.description:
🎺 DON-chan Band Edition 🎸

Play in an ensemble as a team of 4 players! With each player playing a different part, work together to liven up the audience and make the live show a success! 

#TaikonoTatsujin #BandaiNamco
